6. **zero-shot-image-classification** (3293-3303) - tokenizer + processor
7. **object-detection** (3306-3316) - **no tokenizer**, processor only
8. **zero-shot-object-detection** (3318-3328) - tokenizer + processor
9. **document-question-answering** (3330-3340) - tokenizer + processor

